title: Annie's Burger Shack
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Fast food, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Rock pub offering an extensive rock-themed burger menu. Burger can be made veg/vegan upon request and comes with fries/wedges and salad. Sunday roasts and chili dog Tuesday both have a veggie option. Open since May 2009 and was at Navigation Live Music Venue (but the pub itself has a very old history).
